    <p>If you want the exact clinically effective dose with no room for error, this is it. Start here — you can always take 2 gummies (2mg) if 1 is not enough after 5 nights. For full rankings of all melatonin gummies tested, see our <a href="/best-melatonin-gummies/">best melatonin gummies of 2026</a> guide.</p>

